<subSubSection id="C31770F2FF9F8847FF616674BC6BA521" pageId="13" pageNumber="12" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BB22379FF9F8847FF616674BC6BA521" blockId="13.[191,1440,809,869]" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis id="B979FF6BFF9F8847FF616674BF60A506" bold="true" box="[192,324,809,835]" pageId="13" pageNumber="12">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is chosen for the prominent curved crest on the elytral declivity and the prominent pointed granules on other elytral interstriae.
</paragraph>
